Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name GroupId ArtifactId Version Packaging Description
Drombler FX - Parent org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-parent 0.8-SNAPSHOT pom The parent POM of the Drombler FX project. This Drombler FX Parent POM should be the parent (either directly or indirectly) of every Drombler FX project unless there is a good reason to do otherwise (in which case the reason should be documented).
Drombler FX - Startup - Main org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-startup-main 0.8-SNAPSHOT bundle The main classes to startup a Drombler FX based application.
Drombler FX - Core - Application org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-core-application 0.8-SNAPSHOT bundle The core JavaFX-based, modular application framework. It manages the starting and stopping of the JavaFX platform and manages the main application window.
Drombler FX - Core - Data org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-core-data 0.8-SNAPSHOT bundle A JavaFX-based implementation of the Drombler ACP Data Framework.
Drombler FX - Core - Data - L10N - German org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-core-data-l10n-de 0.8-SNAPSHOT bundle L10n (German) of the Drombler FX Data Framework.
Drombler FX - Core - Docking org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-core-docking 0.8-SNAPSHOT bundle A JavaFX-based implementation of the Drombler ACP Docking Framework.
Drombler FX - Core - Docking - L10N - German org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-core-docking-l10n-de 0.8-SNAPSHOT bundle L10n (German) of the JavaFX-based implementation of the Drombler ACP Docking Framework.
Drombler FX - Core - Action org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-core-action 0.8-SNAPSHOT bundle A JavaFX-based implementation of the Drombler ACP Action Framework.
Drombler FX - Core - Standard - Desktop - Classic org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-core-standard-desktop-classic 0.8-SNAPSHOT bundle A classic desktop application layout.

Drombler FX - L10N - All org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-l10n-all 0.8-SNAPSHOT pom L10n of Drombler FX. You can use this POM file e.g. in your dependencies section to manage your Drombler FX L10n dependencies.
Drombler FX - Maven Plugin org.drombler.fx drombler-fx-maven-plugin 0.8-SNAPSHOT maven-plugin The Drombler FX Application Maven Plugin.

Drombler FX org.drombler.fx drombler-fx 0.8-SNAPSHOT pom Drombler FX is a modular Rich Client Platform for JavaFX based on Maven and OSGi. You can use this POM file e.g. in your dependencyManagement section to manage your Drombler FX dependencies.
